name: koi_depth
short_description: Fraction of stellar flux lost at the minimum of the planetary transit

name: koi_ror
selection2_comment: planet radius divided by stellar radius; highly correlated with koi_prad (planet radius)

name: koi_fittype
short_description: Type of Fit for planetary parameters

name: koi_sma
selection2_comment: size of the orbit; highly correlated with koi_period (time between transits)

name: koi_teq
short_description: Approximation for the temperature of the planet

name: koi_insol
short_description: Insolation Flux. This is another way to give the equilibrium temperature

name: koi_dor
selection2_comment: distance between planet and star; highly correlated with koi_period (time between transits)

name: koi_max_sngle_ev
selection2_comment: highly correlated with koi_depth (fraction of stellar flux lost)

name: koi_max_mult_ev
selection2_comment: highly correlated with koi_depth (fraction of stellar flux lost)

name: koi_model_snr
selection2_comment: highly correlated with koi_depth (fraction of stellar flux lost)

name: koi_count
short_description: Number of planet candidates identified in a system

name: koi_num_transits
selection2_comment: number of expected transits; highly correlated with koi_teq (approximate temperature of the planet (whut?))

name: koi_tce_plnt_num
selection2_comment: Planet Number federated to the KOI; highly correlated with koi_count (Number of planet candidates identified in a system)

name: koi_sparprov
short_description: A flag describing the source of the stellar parameters

name: ra
short_description: KIC Right Ascension (equivalent to longitude in maps)

name: dec
short_description: KIC Declination (equivalent to latitude in maps)

name: koi_fwm_sra
selection2_comment: perfectly correlated with dec (KIC Right Ascension)

name: koi_dicco_mra
selection2_comment: image measurement; highly correlated with koi_dikco_mra

name: koi_dicco_mdec
selection2_comment: image measurement; highly correlated with koi_dikco_mdec

name: koi_dicco_msky
selection2_comment: image measurement; highly correlated with koi_dikco_msky
